{"tid":507155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚志源爆袁國強壞習慣 半夜翻煮即食麵","createTime":"2017-12-23T02:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T03:14:48.000Z","uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f72a722dc05e83094fe3d794e1c05261eac1dcb1","tid":507155,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局前局長譚志源早上回應律政司司長袁國強辭職的傳聞時表示，袁國強盡心盡力維護一國兩制，有團隊精神，希望大家對他有較全面評價。他還大爆袁國強的壞習慣，指對方不太照顧身體，會在半夜時翻煮即食麵。<br />\n<br />\n另外，剛當選成為港區人大代表的譚志源，希望自己可以「做好呢份工」，當選後能在更廣闊的平台上處理國家事務，向中央反映香港不同的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n譚志源指出，自己只是一名剛退下來的政府問責官員，沒有政黨背景，對在選舉中獲得的票數及提名票都較預期多感到非常滿意。他不認為全國人大是個橡皮圖章，因憲法給予人大權利及責任，需向人民交代。"},{"pid":"2363467221067583ee1b0897240f8ad8ee995f4e","tid":507155,"uid":42188,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"譚志源竟然將方便麵講成即食麵<br />\n係咪想搞港獨?"},{"pid":"407831b7f262fee7df19141c78ddc2ed02a28997","tid":507155,"uid":49974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"點解佢會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462560b976584b2009dc01dcb01e5e493bc0e81c","tid":507155,"uid":90315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"究竟強國猿係1定0"},{"pid":"be00420613e0f98974e667e74b95168f191761d6","tid":507155,"uid":74851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"407831b7f262fee7df19141c78ddc2ed02a28997","tid":507155,"uid":49974,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"點解佢會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"同居..."},{"pid":"23c57de8b385d68856bbb72a9e567b36c0ab59d7","tid":507155,"uid":86841,"like":